Package: publlama
Title: Query pubmed then feed summaries to LLMs
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Daniel", "Nebdal", , "daniel@nebdal.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Define one or more pubmed queries, and pull down the metadata and
  abstracts for the matching articles. Then define questions to ask an LLM about
  those summaries, and send them to one or more ollama-compatible runners over HTTP.
